#

Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Steamed Broccoli

35 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

healthyeasygrillingchickenvegetable

Description

Succulent grilled chicken marinated in lemon and herbs, served alongside vibrant steamed broccoli for a healthy, flavorful meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
